%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor OWNER as Release Manager

participant UI as QA Checklist UI
participant BFF as Quality Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant QA as Quality Management Service
participant GOV as Governance Consumption Service
participant NS as Notification Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

OWNER->>UI: Open assigned QA item
UI->>BFF: Load QA checklist
BFF->>ORCH: Get checklist context

ORCH->>GOV: Fetch archetype QA checklist
GOV->>READDB: Read governance <br/>checklist or cache lookup
READDB-->>GOV: Checklist items
GOV-->>ORCH: Checklist response

ORCH->>QA: Fetch QA item state
QA->>READDB: Read project_qa_wbs, <br/>project_qa_execution, <br/>project_qa_checklist_execution
READDB-->>QA: QA item detail
QA-->>ORCH: Detail response

ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show checklist and assignee view

OWNER->>UI: Complete checklist,<br/> add comments, <br/>select Pass/Fail, Submit
UI->>BFF: Submit QA outcome
BFF->>ORCH: Start QA outcome flow
ORCH->>QA: Create/update QA execution
QA->>PRIMARYDB: Upsert project_qa_execution
QA->>PRIMARYDB: Upsert project_qa_checklist_execution
QA->>PRIMARYDB: Update project_qa_wbs (qa_status <br/>= Pass/Fail or Submitted for Approval)
QA->>PRIMARYDB: Insert project_qa_status_history
PRIMARYDB-->>QA: Save success
QA-->>ORCH: QA outcome saved
ORCH->>NS: Notify Project Manager / QA Manager
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish QAOutcomeSubmitted Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show updated QA status
